5 個月前\",\"text\":\"Uber Eats外送過來，麵條沒煮熟是怎樣……呈現麵糰狀態，是要客人吃泡在湯裡的麵糰嗎⋯⋯還以為連鎖店至少會有煮麵秒數的SOP，怎麼會連把麵煮熟都做不到？\",\"time\":1734611792,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Daniel Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110148454569549109813/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGTOOjU712ZHQMY1aE6lporlvccQZnXbkojzkZbuwKwsNy9pEv-g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"20240521,23 周年牛肉麵一碗99元，來吃了兩天。肉不少，湯也不錯。就是盛辣椒、酸菜的碟子上面有油漬像沒洗乾淨。\",\"time\":1716463563,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Hsiu-Haung Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106258726867058020542/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXojWQbqNP_xmWUrZDvjNh7zC0_7pLOdVhFhat-TQ6iqeisoeqT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"趁四十週年慶祝特價來吃牛肉麵。雖然價格親民，但是整體感受不是很好。首先牛肉麵的肉很硬很難咬，麵跟菜也就一般水平。唯一好的是湯，味道很棒。\\n人員服務上，剛好遇上一波客人比較多的狀況，但不知道為什麼前場除負責點餐的店員外，其他人都沒有在處理收餐盤與清潔。連到我餐點上來之後，前個客人的碗盤都還在桌上。\\n雖然最近週年慶會比較忙，可以理解。不過這樣水平，真的是吃附近的麵食館可能還比較好。\",\"time\":1702698433,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNRIxguZcNfa2533O2ouPgX1ODhHXzf4pFSXWYzqZ0G56oyRLvyAg8J8vzs4wAV0Y-e04lLsGvGlW8e9mvR9AwrriIGqX5CWfxSNss2-3a4iUZV-HR0qIGg_U273EfOxFG-BrHeI2gJYgjoEgYv6Qt96O6FdqoH9KqjeWduceQ0iPWJd8TR9s3wFmueyEiNH0vaY-X2eUA8MaPB0UoqocLENY3I-_ymJasZAO6eOKceqTAPWb2MzseCJ0SbgsBqrY5PzzLMafTTYhdTbuqxJvqAPnXcQac2aESmZpDW_ZWeYlCkLa2hoHCM0pnuth0SIXF0CaA7sGLZbns1AaQhuNt283_0_Lk4aQiksKDZxXMrNIZXH8gPNWM8-IobEsEEbdPzJXbOYoSJtqYzY4EKLHcm_MWClq_N8LA6FYy_7MbayyHaU6qlywkP59HJZjTjDrnAtH5W2qfxW8sK3z-3Eren24_NKml1qACPjvON8kieptRYmGw13z1A_bM1pBt0Gd4k_vRImsHvRQj7oeQpRT4Uzjt_DvroM4JxYwLEXXwYn9yAcBn-foke-A0P0wd4ITBEUjLPHHL7xneQ-edSsPLS-swgUwuirNl329nhWjPk0YwEBgXikA3lJe6IftGiSAoz_zQwB\",\"AXQCQNRF5IlcH9_p3NEZATrOtIIRn2AFjGN4esKLt3lgRPIU-JVy2MK-T_J1Bz7WC5Dp8SW8INjkObaXSgvq4DnO74iSJfEDI3nAyINFEfVmlI41_4-swQFxb3dJaf